        "text": "; rather, as in the margin, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "a secret speech",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", or ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "a low whisper",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (Kay); comp. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Isaiah 29:4",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The word elsewhere means \"the muttering of a ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
